THIS IS A PLACEHOLDER — REPLACE BEFORE FINAL SUBMISSION
=========================================================

Replace this file with your group's actual presentation PDF.

File name:  presentation.pdf  (keep this exact name)
Format:     PDF
Content:    Slide deck used for the group presentation
            (PowerPoint exported to PDF, LaTeX Beamer, Google Slides, etc.)

How to replace:
  1. Delete this file
  2. Copy your real PDF here with the name "presentation.pdf"
  3. git add presentation.pdf
  4. git commit -m "add final presentation PDF"
  5. git push origin main
